item.description: 測試開始 第一題 : \[ f(x) = \sin(x) \] 第二題 : When \(a \ne 0\), there are two solutions to \(ax^2 + bx + c = 0\) and they are: \(x = {-b \pm \sqrt{b^2-4ac} \over 2a}\) END
